				\begin{document}$$\,\hbox {TeV}$$\end{document}. The performance of these algorithms is measured in most cases with Z\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
