				\begin{document}$${\tau _{\mathrm{had}{\text {-}}\mathrm{vis}}}$$\end{document}reconstruction and identification algorithms is presented in Sect. 3, and the trigger and offline energy calibration algorithms are discussed in Sect. 5.

