				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$|\eta | < 1.8$$\end{document}. Hadron calorimetry is based on different detector technologies, with scintillator tiles (|η|<1.7\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
